Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我来点灯\NLet me light the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到靴子了\NI've misplaced my boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它们放在楼下厨房门边上了\NI put them downstairs by the kitchen door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡着了…\NI was asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当你拿走它们的时候\Nwhen you took them and did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,－是的 你想让我别那么做么？－不\N-Yes. Would you rather I not? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想昨晚上醒着以便我们能聊聊\NOnly I had intended to be awake last night so we could talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,聊聊我们要何去何从\Nwhich, what with how it's been, we have not done...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个自你到达之后的如人所愿的平静的夜晚\Nin the peace of the evening as I would like, since your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢静静的谈话 比如白天过后的晚上\NI would enjoy to converse in the stillness, after the day, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我会准备两杯咖啡 我就不会睡着了\NTonight, I will have two cups of coffee, and I will not fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,早上\NIn the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始一天的工作前的这段时间\Nin the quiet before we each take up our work...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也是一段不错的谈话时间\Nis also a pleasant occasion for such intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上你想开始这个谈话么？\NWould you like to start a discussion this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想打扰到孩子\NI wouldn't want to disturb the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,William正熟睡中呢\NWilliam sleeps soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,若你愿意请关上卧室门 Bullock先生？\NIf you will see to the bedroom door, Mr Bullock?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了他？\NHave I killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 死人不会颤抖\NFirst, the dead don't shiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其次 你只是做了他让你做的事\NAnd next, you just done what he asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,导致他到如此地步的原因\NAnd ain't it more likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,更可能是他下体的疾病\Nwhat turned him worse is underlying woe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是试图减轻他的痛苦而插入肛门的手指\Nthan a thumb up his ass attempting his fucking relief?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 出去吧\NGo on, get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你是干什么的？\NWhat's your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Francis Wolcott\NI'm Francis Wolcott.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Ellsworth,Francis Wolcott先生\NMy name's Ellsworth, Mr Francis Wolcott.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,－你能听到我说话么？－当然 先生 你好？\N-Can you hear me? -Yes, sir. How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-我还好 很高兴你能听明白 －是的 先生\N-I'm well. Glad you make me out. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 在GARRET夫人的地盘上未被准允的\NBecause them as poke around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,闲逛的行为\NMs Garret's workings without a by-your-leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是不被受欢迎的 WOLCOTT先生\Nain't welcome, Mr Wolcott...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不应该再延续你的错误了\Nand you ought not to repeat your fucking mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,WELL 无知者无罪\NWell, that's an uncivil response to an innocent error.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你年轻的时候是在康斯托克工作么？\NDid you work in the Comstock when you was beardless?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为George Hearst先生看管生意么？\NFor Mr George Hearst, has a keen eye for the colour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当Hearst先生的地质专家\NAs a geologist for Mr Hearst.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,WELL 你比我优秀 Ellsworth先生\NWell, you have the advantage of me, Mr Ellsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那就有点扯了 WOLCOTT\NThat ain't a possibility, Wolcott.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有一个错误是无辜的\NNo more than an error of yours would be innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我大致上想起了一个叫Ellsworth的人\NI do dimly recall an Ellsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(298,36)}[consolidated Virginia\统一弗基尼亚公司]我认为是这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他管理统一弗基尼亚公司的运营\NSuperintended the consolidated Virginia operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会给你答复的\NI don't give a fuck what you recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是个英雄 没是没夜地挖了一周\NA hero. Dug a week without respite...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,从塌方中救了三个人\Nto save three poor souls from the cave-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以及46具尸体 从一个就不应该开采的矿洞里\NAnd 46 corpses in a fucking hole that ought never to have been dug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,人总得选择 在计算了收益和风险之后\NAlways a choice, to count the saved or lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,给我离开这里\NGet off this property!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅当个反对必然变革的人\NJust as a man opposed to inevitable change...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不一定就是勒德分子\Nneedn't invariably be called a Luddite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,另一种描述的可能更贴切点\NAnother choice might be simply to describe him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,比如他适应的慢\Nas slow in his processes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉你的老板 他派来的下个代理人\NYou tell that cocksucker you work for, the next surrogate he sends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不应该是来自康斯托克\Noughtn't to be bloodied from the Comstock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,噪音有点大 不是么 Ellsworth先生？\NThe noise is terrible, isn't it, Mr Ellsworth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就像命运一样\NLike fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ox, box, fox."\N"Ox, box, fox."
