Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(298,36)}[意指索菲亚没一心一意的学习\NNora是那个布娃娃]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,NORA的注意力没集中\NNora's attentions are wandering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是你 我就给她一块糖\NIf I were you, I'd bribe her with candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请进  lsringhausen小姐\NPlease come in, Miss lsringhausen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你坐么？\NWill you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 你还坚持你的想法 想辞退我？\NDo you remain of a mind, ma'am, to dispense with my services?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我很尊敬你的教育能力和专业素养\NI have immense respect for your training and intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isringhausen小姐\NMiss lsringhausen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也很感激你在教育Sofia上倾注的心血\Nand gratitude for your efforts toward Sofia's education.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,性格上 我和你不太合\NI am ill-suited temperamentally to collaborate with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,处在你我的位置上的女人大概都会如此\Nas women in our positions must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我提议给你六个月工资的解雇费\NI propose to pay you six months' wages severance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,和额外的200美元以抵偿\Nand an additional $200 against...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你来回的费用\Nthe expense for your journey here and return to Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在你在此等待安排期间\NWhile you're making your arrangements...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会继续支付你在旅馆的房费\NI will also continue to pay for your room here at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些条款而言 Garret夫人\NAs to those terms, Mrs Garret,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的提议非常合理\Nyour behaviour is very fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,lsringhausen小姐 Cotton Mather本来会发现\NMiss lsringhausen, Cotton Mather would have found...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这些艰难和不愉快的\Nhard and joyless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你如此坚定地施加于\Nthe standards you so resolutely apply to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我和Sofia之上的评判准则\Nme and Sofia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以及 当然 还有评判你自己的标准\Nand, of course, to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我祝福你\NI wish you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢 夫人\NThank you, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,－你要…  －我不和Sofia道别了\N-Would you… -I'll not say goodbye to Sofia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,以免她伤心\Nto spare her upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dan.  -E.B.\N-Dan.  -E.B.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,－来点咖啡？ －好的\N-Coffee? -Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我就直说了 Dan\NI'll be candid, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚我没睡好\NI did not sleep well last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了从AI房间传出的惨叫\NI heard screaming from Al's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,许多个晚上都有过这情况\NHappens up there many a fucking evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well  这次是AI在惨叫 Dan\NWell, Al was fucking screaming, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好奇他今早怎么样了\NAnd I'm wondering how he's feeling this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,并且你围着那儿绕来绕去 并没有减轻我的担心\NAnd you dancing around the pole ain't allaying my fucking anxieties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well  你现在听到他惨叫了么？\NWell, do you hear any screams from him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 沉默也不是证据\NSilence ain't proof either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别和我争论 E.B. 否则我扇你个傻逼\NTake no tongue with me, E.B., or I'll slap you fucking silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他在恢复中 而且还不能接见人\NHe's on the mend and he ain't fucking receiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 那就是我问的原因\NWell, that's all I was fucking asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,－那么那就是你的答案 －请传达我的好意\N-Then that's your fucking answer. -Convey my joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,并且告诉他数不尽的好事在等着他呢\NAnd tell him numerous scores await.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,温暖的一天  Dan？\NSoft-fucking day, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Crop Ear 早上好\NMorning, Crop Ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 Eamon\NSorry, Eamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(298,36)}[他叫的是那个人的外号]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看看 这儿不是重新长出来了么？\NTake a good look. Ain't growing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,－他怎么样了？ －AI早上出去了\N-ls he about? -Al's out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,去Gayville看个地方\NLook at a place in Gayville.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah？\NOh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要抓住眼前的运气 Dan\NYou must seize fortune by the forelock, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我来这儿的原因\NThat's why I'm here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把一件美事送到他的面前\Nto put a matter before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,－你知道的 我不会浪费他的时间的\NYou know I'll not waste the man's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,－是的 你不会\N-No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是有你的办法 Dan\NThat's some fucking way you have about you, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你要么告诉我们俩你的事\NNow, you could either say your piece to me and Johnny...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要么就滚出这里\Nor you can get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我会很高兴地说这事\NI'll say it gladly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你会把我的话递给他\Nand hope you'll commend my words to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个在Gayville的人 要在第一时间告诉\Nwho's in Gayville, at the earliest opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我在酝酿一场行动\NI contemplate a piece of activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要找几个可靠的人\NI need to organise some reliable fellows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,埋伏在合适的地方伏击黄金运输队\NIocate a right place to waylay that metal.
