Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.32,0:27:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 我感觉你们最好准备一下\NWell, I guess you better go make ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.84,0:27:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.68,0:27:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 和我来 Johnny.\NAll right. Come with me, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.08,0:27:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,－帮我生火 －当然可以 医生\N-Help me with this stove. -Sure. Sure, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.04,0:27:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在新条约签订前的土地和工作证明\NAs to claims filed and worked prior to the new treaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.80,0:27:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大体上从山区仍归苏族所有的时间开始算起\Nin essence from when the hills still belonged to the Sioux...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.88,0:27:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对其合法性的推测是 会依然\Nthe presumption of legitimacy will apply...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.48,0:27:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,赋予其效力 以便缓和事态\Nsubject to qualification, according to mitigating facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.64,0:27:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,简单来讲 没有援引控制原则的情况下\NIn short, with no controlling principle being invoked...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.64,0:27:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(298,36)}[我感觉这个原则就是所谓的谁发现就归谁的公认准则]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.80,0:27:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所有权就会视情况而定\Ntitle will be determined on a case-by-case basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.72,0:27:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,当土地证明被推翻 新的所有权\NWhen claims are overturned, new title
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.14,0:27:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就会以说好的价格发放\Nwill be awarded at said prices...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.96,0:28:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,通过抽签 给那些允许提交合法申请的人\Nvia lottery, to those submitting verified offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.16,0:28:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望地方政府要排除在资格之外\NI only hope territorial officials will be excluded from eligibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.56,0:28:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.72,0:28:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最好告诉你的朋友和亲戚\NBetter tell your friends and relatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.48,0:28:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(298,36)}[希望官员亲属也不要参与]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.48,0:28:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们的幸运服也要在画卷之外\Nto pick their lucky suits out for that drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.60,0:28:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅在Wolcott先生的朋友亲戚这样做了之后\NOnly after Mr Wolcott's have picked out theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.36,0:28:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我预计即将到来的司法支持\NOf course, anticipation of the forthcoming judicial holding...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.12,0:28:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会很大程度上净化市场\Nmay itself largely cleanse the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.92,0:28:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,保持市场的畅通总是更可取的\NIt's always preferable to allow the market to operate unimpeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.48,0:28:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们赞成让我说的话\NWould that argue for allowing word of my presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.48,0:28:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在营地里流传几天么 在我本人正式现身之前？\Nto circulate a bit before presenting myself officially?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.92,0:28:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用这段时间熏跑一些人\NMan might use that time to put some stink on his johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.44,0:28:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.04,0:28:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这呢 在柜台后面\NDown here. Behind the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.60,0:28:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,盘点库存\NTaking inventory.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.16,0:28:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天上不了课\NI can't do a lesson today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.52,0:29:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.40,0:29:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他病得太厉害了\NHe's too sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.52,0:29:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能会死 我不能留下来\NMaybe he'll fucking die. But I can't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.84,0:29:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是可能留下来学习计算利润明智点\NBut it'd be smart to stay and learn to calculate fucking interest...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.44,0:29:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在通融票据上以及那些贴现票据上\Non that accommodation paper and those fucking discount notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.04,0:29:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,或者其他的什么东西\Nand whatever the fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.68,0:29:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,换个时间吧 没事的 Trixie.\NAnother time. It's fine, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.60,0:29:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,－我弄疼你的肩了么？ －没有\N-Did I hurt your shoulder? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.52,0:29:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了\NI gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.52,0:29:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想出去一会儿么？\NWant to go out for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.12,0:29:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她说Swearengen境况很差\NShe says Swearengen's bad off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚我听到他一次次的惨叫\NLast night I heard him screaming out again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.16,0:29:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜他越来越糟了\NI guess he's worsened with the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.04,0:30:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你给孩子园艺工具\NThanks for outfitting the boy with garden equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.64,0:30:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他计划回馈我点收成\NHe's planning to take some prizes come harvest fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.52,0:30:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他提到了玉米和南瓜\NHe mentioned corn and squash, both.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.60,0:30:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我有丹佛的消息\NI had some news from Denver...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.92,0:30:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我们银行的提议\Nconcerning our proposal on the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.96,0:30:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要提供注册资本的15%\NWe'd need to find 1 5% of our proposed capitalisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.28,0:30:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们注册两百万我们就要\NIf we capitalise at the $2 million we figured on--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.40,0:30:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,30万,和丹佛承诺的分开来算\N$300,000 separate from what Denver will underwrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.68,0:30:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他们以Garret账户做为抵押\NOr they'd credit Mrs Garret's accounts as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.48,0:30:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不能那么做\NNot doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.88,0:30:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我没提议\NI don't advocate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.00,0:30:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我正要告诉你是他们主动提出的\NI'm informing you of a communication they volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.84,0:30:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能那么做\NWe're not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.96,0:30:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我要自己掏腰包了\NSuppose I'll have to dip into my own kit, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.28,0:30:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,即使这样 到头来还是要剪掉我的头发\NEven so, it's back to cutting my own hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.60,0:30:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想个办法的\NI'll take the idea around.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.72,0:30:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Swearengen会出钱的\NSwearengen would put it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.40,0:30:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,臭名昭著的人\NFucking reputable people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.08,0:30:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果钱在流通前必须是干净的\NIf money had to be clean before it was recirculated...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.80,0:30:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在还生活在山洞里\Nwe'd still be living in fucking caves.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.16,0:30:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,－你家老头了说的？ －我说的\N-Your old man? -Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.88,0:30:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,李先生独家为你提供鸦片\NMr Lee will provide opium to you exclusively...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.00,0:30:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,以便卖给营地里的白人\Nfor sale to whites in the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.84,0:30:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你会得到Celestial's Alley赌博\NYou will receive 50% of the gaming proceeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.84,0:30:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(298,36)}[Celestial's Alley应该指中国人的聚居区]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.96,0:31:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,收益的一半\Nfrom Celestial's Alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.24,0:31:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人会监管收益\NMy men will lamp the take.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.00,0:31:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在这解释做生意艰难会劳烦李先生的\NIt will spare Mr Lee here explaining how slow business was...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.32,0:31:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,比如由于佛陀婚礼记念日什么的\N'cause of Buddha's wedding anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.68,0:31:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人监管收益\NYour men lamp the take...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也包括Celestial的妓女生意\Nalso on proceeds from Celestial prostitutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.28,0:31:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,－你想要多少妓女？ －你能带来多少？\N-How many do you want? -How many can you bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.56,0:31:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多少？\NHow many?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.72,0:31:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来好像你有无尽的供应似的\NThat sounds like a man with an inexhaustible supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.92,0:31:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多少英国货 我的朋友？\NHow much English do you have, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.48,0:31:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该加深下了解\NMaybe when we get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.28,0:31:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要12个 我不要被干过的\NI'll take a dozen, and I don't want them fucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我定价格 维持费用你付\NI set the rates. The upkeep's on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.88,0:31:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为维持费用是很低的\NAnd my understanding is the upkeep is quite minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.72,0:31:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 那就让他多拿点去打麻将吧\NGood! Gives him more to spend on mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.48,0:31:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不问我们的安排中的偏袒了\NI won't question the apparent one-sidedness of our arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.20,0:31:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你也不是李先生单独安排的\NThe arrangement is not yours and Mr Lee's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.72,0:31:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 在我不了解的方法上\NYes, and in ways I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.56,0:32:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让李先生在营地 肯定是让你\Nit must benefit you and the man whose name I must never say...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.48,0:32:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,以及那位不能提名字的人获益了\Nto have Mr Lee in camp...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.36,0:32:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吴先生要出局了\Nand perhaps Mr Wu out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.72,0:32:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会去见他的祖宗们\Nmaybe among the spirits of his ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.52,0:32:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不管怎样祝福我 我都知道 最后都会到\NBut what a blessing for me, finally to reach a point in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.32,0:32:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那个我感觉不到的 生命的终点\Nwhere I don't feel I have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.40,0:32:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一个后肢行走的动物\NA creature walking around on hind legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.80,0:32:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像Crop Ear和六个伐木工那样\NJust like Crop Ear and them half-dozen bushwhackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.96,0:32:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在森林里游荡\Nout in the forests...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.20,0:32:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一伙我喜欢或不喜欢的人 充斥着我每天的生活\Nones I'd fall in with or out, whatever suited my daily purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.52,0:32:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,直到后来我遇到了AI\NThat's what I was till I crossed paths with Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.00,0:32:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 敲鼓弹琴吧 我会撕点衣服装点你\NWell, bang the drum and play the pipes and I'll rend our fucking garments.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.00,0:32:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是说说\NI was just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.76,0:32:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下午我不想听忏悔\NI ain't hearing confessions this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.64,0:33:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,答应我 你会和我一起烧了这里 Dan\NSay you'll burn it down with me, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.72,0:33:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.76,0:33:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个该死的地方\NThis fucking place...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.80,0:33:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在Tolliver占有它之前\Nbefore letting Tolliver take it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.48,0:33:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NDone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.60,0:33:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,Jewel,张嘴说点\NWell, open your mouth, Jewel, and say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们听不懂的事吧\Nwe can't fucking understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.92,0:33:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他在叫你\NHe's asking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.00,0:33:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别和你的秘密一起死掉\NDon't die with your fucking secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.68,0:33:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,清理三号房 Dolly说她流血了\NClean the number three. Dolly said she bled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.00,0:33:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\NGod damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.60,0:34:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要来点威士忌 医生你要么？\NI may get me a whiskey, Doc. You need any whiskey?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.44,0:34:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不要威士忌\NNo, I do not want a fucking whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.88,0:34:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,也许能稳定你的手\NWell, maybe as far as steadying the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.24,0:34:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么敢这样和我说话！ 闭嘴\NHow dare you? You shut your fucking mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.12,0:34:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我没讽刺什么\NI didn't mean nothing by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.08,0:34:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,威士忌不会稳定我的手\NWhiskey does not steady the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.32,0:34:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是降低了对我的手是否颤抖的担心而已\NIt just dulls the worry over the hand's unsteadiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.56,0:34:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 上帝啊 我不想杀了他\NJesus Christ! Jesus Christ, I do not need to kill another man!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.28,0:34:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,擦\NFuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.56,0:34:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的医药包的左上角\NTop left corner of my fucking bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.80,0:34:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,找什么？\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.40,0:34:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,香油 你的白痴 减轻你烫伤的持续疼痛\NBalm, you fucking idiot, against the burn you fucking just sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.52,0:34:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 医生\NThanks, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.96,0:34:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.72,0:35:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dan -走开 吴\N-Dan. -Go away, Wu.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.60,0:35:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Swearengen. -没门\N-Swearengen. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.72,0:35:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Swearengen. -Well  不会让你上去的\N-Swearengen. -Well, it ain't gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.32,0:35:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Swearengen. -不  吴  他生病了\N-Swearengen. -No, Wu! He's fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.76,0:35:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 AI不能和你讲话 我也不明白你在说啥\NNow, Al can't talk to you right now, and I can't understand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.60,0:35:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你回Chink Alley吧\Nso you go the fuck back to Chink Alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.12,0:35:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,别凭空瞎画 对我胡言乱语\NDo not start drawing air to talk gibberish to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.60,0:35:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\NCocksucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.16,0:35:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-看在上帝的份上 -混蛋\N-For Christ's sake. -Cocksucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在浪费我的时间  吴\NIt's wasted on me, Wu.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.28,0:35:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋  混蛋\NCocksucker! Cocksucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.72,0:35:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白你的意思  吴  我没AI那么聪明\NI don't get it, Wu. I am not as smart as Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.60,0:35:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有太多事等着我们去做呢\NAnd there's too much on our fucking plate right now to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.44,0:35:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-混蛋 旧金山  -上帝啊\N-Cocksucker! San Francisco. -Jesus fucking Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.48,0:35:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 有个看不到的混蛋在你旁边\NAll right, there's an invisible cocksucker next to you...
